OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782841688
OL,3,C#120,000 fine for Blackpool Hotel
OL,4,Cafter boy is electrocuted
OL,6,FThe owners of a Blackpool hotel where
OL,7,Fa child died after suffering an
OL,8,Felectric shock has been fined #120,000.
OL,10,FBlackpool Council successfully brought
OL,11,Fcharges against Y7 Hotels Ltd, owner
OL,12,Fof the Tiffany Hotel on North
OL,13,FPromenade, for health and safety
OL,14,Foffences.
OL,16,FIn September 2023, Jack Piper-Sheach,
OL,17,F10, suffered an electric shock in the
OL,18,Freception area of the hotel and died
OL,19,Fin hospital four days later.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
