OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782841688
OL,3,C#120,000 fine for Blackpool Hotel
OL,4,Cafter boy is electrocuted
OL,6,FHe and his family had been visiting
OL,7,FBlackpool from Lincolnshire.
OL,8,FInvestigations were launched by
OL,9,FLancashire Police and Blackpool
OL,10,FCouncil.
OL,12,FLancashire Police found no criminal
OL,13,Fcase to answer, but Blackpool Council
OL,14,Flater brought charges against Y7
OL,15,FHotels Ltd for offences contrary to
OL,16,Fthe Health and Safety at Work Act 1974.
OL,18,FNone of the charges related to Jack's
OL,19,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782841688
OL,3,C#120,000 fine for Blackpool Hotel
OL,4,Cafter boy is electrocuted
OL,6,FRepresentatives of the business
OL,7,Fattended Preston Crown Court on
OL,8,FWednesday 15 April 2026 and entered a
OL,9,Fguilty plea to two offences, in
OL,10,Frelation to the Tiffany Hotel,
OL,11,FBlackpool.
OL,13,FAt a sentencing hearing on Friday 26
OL,14,FJune, Y7 Hotels Ltd was fined #120,000
OL,15,Fand ordered to pay #24,000 costs to
OL,16,FBlackpool Council.
OL,18,FCllr Dave Flanagan, Blackpool Council
OL,19,Fcabinet member for housing, empty
OL,20,Fproperties and public protection, said:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782841688
OL,3,C#120,000 fine for Blackpool Hotel
OL,4,Cafter boy is electrocuted
OL,6,F"This is a tragic case and throughout
OL,7,Four investigation our thoughts have
OL,8,Falways been, and continue be with, the
OL,9,Ffamily, friends and loved ones of Jack
OL,10,FPiper-Sheach."
OL,12,FBlackpool Council launched an
OL,13,Finvestigation into the hotel in late
OL,14,F2023. Inspectors found that essential
OL,15,Fremedial works to correct dangerous
OL,16,Felectrical installations were not
OL,17,Fundertaken by a competent, qualified
OL,18,Felectrician, nor were any works
OL,19,Fdocumented or certified.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782841688
OL,3,C#120,000 fine for Blackpool Hotel
OL,4,Cafter boy is electrocuted
OL,6,FAn electrical installation condition
OL,7,Freport (EICR) from 2020 had documented
OL,8,Fissues of concern that posed a danger
OL,9,Fto guests and employees of the hotel.
OL,11,FFollowing that stage of the council's
OL,12,Finvestigation, the director of Tiffany
OL,13,FHotel agreed to voluntarily close.
OL,15,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,16,Fthen sent in two specialist inspectors
OL,17,Fto further assess the electrical
OL,18,Finstallation. They found three more,
OL,19,Fseparate dangerous areas within the
OL,20,Fhotel.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782841688
OL,3,C#120,000 fine for Blackpool Hotel
OL,4,Cafter boy is electrocuted
OL,6,FTheir report concluded that the
OL,7,Felectrical installation was not
OL,8,Fmaintained in a satisfactory
OL,9,Fcondition, putting employees and
OL,10,Fguests at risk of fatal injuries.
OL,12,FAn Improvement Notice was served and
OL,13,Fin November 2023, a satisfactory EICR
OL,14,Fwas provided. Council officers carried
OL,15,Fout a follow-up inspection to ensure
OL,16,Fspecified works had been undertaken
OL,17,Fand the hotel was later permitted to
OL,18,Freopen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782841688
OL,3,C#120,000 fine for Blackpool Hotel
OL,4,Cafter boy is electrocuted
OL,6,FCllr Flanagan added: "This case should
OL,7,Fserve as a wake-up call for all
OL,8,Fhoteliers and business owners ` not
OL,9,Fjust in Blackpool. They have a duty of
OL,10,Fcare to ensure their electrical
OL,11,Finstallation is regularly reviewed and
OL,12,Fall remedial works are completed
OL,13,Fproperly and swiftly by competent,
OL,14,Fqualified electricians, and documented
OL,15,For certified appropriately.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782841688
OL,3,C#120,000 fine for Blackpool Hotel
OL,4,Cafter boy is electrocuted
OL,6,F"Every employer has a legal duty to
OL,7,Fensure the health, safety and welfare
OL,8,Fof their employees and the public. Our
OL,9,FHealth and Safety Team investigate any
OL,10,Fbreaches of health and safety
OL,11,Fregulations and take action where
OL,12,Fneeded.
OL,14,F"When a serious breach is identified,
OL,15,Fwe will not hesitate to hold those
OL,16,Fresponsible to account. I'd like to
OL,17,Fthank our teams for their thorough
OL,18,Fapproach to this investigation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
